descMeta.description:
Harrison Paul Porter (1921-2012), a nephew of Katherine Anne
          Porter, was her legal guardian from 1977 to 1980. His papers include correspondence;
          guardianship records; published materials and notes; audiovisual materials; memorabilia;
          and photographs documenting Porter's relationship with his aunt and her literary career
          and reputation. Significant individuals represented in the collection include Robert Penn
          Warren, Seymour Lawrence, and Joan Daves.
